# Runner-provisioned agent scaffolding. On every agent spawn the runner copies
# qontinui-claude-config/.claude/agents/*.md into each worktree's .claude/agents/
# so named subagents resolve. It is machine state, never source — but because it
# is untracked it makes `git status` report every agent worktree dirty, which
# trips the worktree-reclaim G1 "never remove a dirty worktree" gate and blocks
# reclaim. Matches qontinui-runner and qontinui-web, which already ignore it.
.claude/

